# Tailwind standalone CLI binary — platform-specific, not committed
# Download from: https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss/releases
/tailwindcss
/tailwindcss-*
# public/css/app.css IS committed — it is the compiled output that DreamHost uses
